{"word":"G5420 - φράσσω - phrássō - fras'-so - Stop","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φράσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phrássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">fras'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Stop</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அடை, நீங்கு"},{"paragraph":"to fence in, block up, stop up, close up to put to silence"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently a strengthened form of the base of <a href=\"#/G5424 - φρήν - phrḗn - frane/5424\">G5424</a>; to <i>fence</i> or inclose, that is, (specifically) to <i>block</i> up (figuratively to <i>silence</i>): - stop.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}